          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel and finely dice the<strong> carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic </strong></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
